thread.title: James Beckner
thread.title_full: Kitco Metals Inc. reviewed by James Beckner

author: James Beckner
title: James Beckner
text: 1/4 oz gold American Eagle was received in a timely manner. The coin was in excellent shape with the felt holder. The random year I received was 1995, a very significant date for me. I am quite satisfied with the service and product. The young lady at checkout was super helpful at working out the details. Rate 5 stars.
